; 'examinar.i'
; ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
; We'll skip 'examine' since it's not blocked! (see previous tests)
; ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
; @NOTE: The busca/mira syntax variations/synonyms are not available!
;        See annotated source comments and proposed fixes.
; ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
